    "As neural network topologies and datasets get increasingly complicated, the quest for innovative optimization algorithms remains an important field of study to increase training efficiency and model generalization.In brief, regularization approaches such as Dropout and L1/L2 regularization minimize overfitting by applying penalties to the loss function, hence increasing generalization in neural networks.",
